data.description: Awesome Cottage style home in gated community---55+ active adult living. Front porch for sitting and relaxing. Open flowing floorplan with soaring ceilings and skylights. Your guests will amazed as they enter into the foyer flanked by a muti-purpose area. Office, craft room, library, sitting room---make it your own. Fireplace Great room open to the kitchen and dining area. Gleaming hardwood floors and carpet in the bedrooms. The kitchen boasts of stainless steel appliances, pantry and granite countertops. A chefs delight! The owner's retreat with large walk=in closet and en-suite bath. Large secondary bedroom and bath---Wow! The community clubhouse with a pool, fitness center for your enjoyment. This is a must see property-----YOUR SEARCH IS OVER!
